                Riconoscere la plastica per smaltirla al meglio

di M.Cristina Ceresa -                      24 Aprile 2026

<iframe class="td-youtube-player" width="600" height="560" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/c9bH8igI5WA?enablejsapi=1&feature=oembed&wmode=opaque&vq=hd720&&&" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay"></iframe>                            


